text: Hey Makara, you have submitted correctly. I am seeing the submissions on both our MKPL and the DevPost side. Thank you.

<@U2H3TT8F2> Hi i have 1 more question.
can i update some code while pending review?
Yep you can update. You would just be re-listing the asset since its already been pending. You have until 11:59PM EST to do it. You should be ok from the DevPost end (no changes needed there)
<@U2H3TT8F2> so that mean i remove my submit listing and submit again? or just edit theme
You would need to remove your listing (as it was not reviewed yet) and then re-add it with the new updates :slightly_smiling_face:
